column14:
'desc': [u'

Littles Deluxe Gift Set Price: Rs.200

New-born babies are welcomed to the world in a grand and fashionable manner with celebrations in the form of shopping sprees to buy them new gifts and accessories. The Deluxe Gift Set from Littles is one such gift set
column15:
which is ideally made for babies and contains products that will be useful for them during their growth period.

\r\n

\r\n\tThis Littles Deluxe Gift Set contains 1 Royal Maxi Feeding Bottle
column16: which you can use to feed your baby milk or water once they are out of the breast-feeding stage. The cute
column17: little rattle makes entertaining sounds intriguing the baby
column18: and stimulating their audio senses. To tend to the uneasiness and discomfort felt in the period of their teeth growing
column19: the babies can use the Teether to help soothe the gums and relax them. With fun and colourful accessories
column20:
this Littles Deluxe Gift Set makes an ideal gift for the baby for any occasion and can conveniently be gifted to both girls and boys.

\n
